msgstr "Disabled: the main site must have Vigilante's custom-login configured."

#. translators: %s: missatge d'error de validació
#: includes/class-vigsync-plugin.php:84
msgid "Després d'actualitzar Vigilante Network Sync, l'esquema de Vigilante no s'ha pogut validar (%s). S'ha desactivat el redirect de login per precaució. Revisa la configuració."
msgstr "After updating Vigilante Network Sync, Vigilante's schema could not be validated (%s). The login redirect has been disabled as a precaution. Please review the configuration."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:182
msgid "Detall"
msgstr "Details"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:115
msgid "El site del qual es llegeix la configuració de Vigilante. Per defecte, el principal de la xarxa (normalment #1)."
msgstr "The site whose Vigilante configuration is read. Defaults to the network's main site (usually #1)."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:52
msgid "El site principal desat ja no existeix; s'ha aplicat el principal de la xarxa per defecte. Reviseu-ho a sota."
msgstr "The saved main site no longer exists; the network's default main site has been applied. Please review below."

#. translators: %s: URL de login del principal
#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:146
msgid "Els logins dels subsites es redirigiran a: %s"
msgstr "Subsite logins will be redirected to: %s"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:155
msgid "Email d'avisos"
msgstr "Notification email"

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:195
msgid "Error"
msgstr "Error"

