msgid "No tens permisos per fer aquesta acció."
msgstr "You don't have permission to perform this action."

#: includes/class-vigsync-network-admin.php:140
msgid "Nota: el redirect de login no s'ha activat perquè el site principal no té el custom-login de Vigilante configurat."
msgstr "Note: the login redirect was not enabled because the main site does not have Vigilante's custom-login configured."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:129
msgid "Per defecte es preserven les llistes d'IPs i la CSP report-uri de cada site (camps específics per site)."
msgstr "By default, each site's IP lists and CSP report-uri are preserved (site-specific fields)."

#: includes/views/network-settings-page.php:158
msgid "Rebrà un avís quan Vigilante canviï de versió (un cop per versió)."
msgstr "Will receive a notice when Vigilante changes version (once per version)."

